main event: A brighter object estimated at 10,000 feet was observed over Omaha, Nebraska by Clare Fenner and his wife, leaving a bright trail behind.
interesting points: The sighting occurred late at night, around 10 p.m.,The object appeared to be moving at a fast trajectory,The object left a very bright and visible trail,The sighting lasted for several minutes,This report is part of a documented investigation by the U.S. Air Force's Project Blue Book.
sighted object: a brilliant light in the sky
